rescueLines.line: Marcus, what are you doing here?
I was just finishing these guys off when you came in.
So what, did you stop to sharpen your axe?
You and Eileen, always making fun of me. Where is she, by the way?
We could sure use her healing. Let's pay her a visit.
The demon Magroth tore the town apart.
Magroth! The demon of the Severed Mountain!
